{"type":"message","id":"ea862b70","parentId":"d2dea2cf","timestamp":"2026-03-05T14:30:22.597Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经获取了技能文件和注册表信息。现在我了解了：\n\n已有的Skills（第一批次）：\n1. config-format-converter - 配置文件格式转换\n2. batch-file-renamer - 批量文件重命名\n3. qr-code-tool - 二维码生成\n4. rest-api-tester - API测试\n5. timestamp-converter - 时间戳转换\n\n需要生成第二批次，5个完全不同的高价值Skills。现在我需要：\n1. 创建 batch-2026-03-05-2 目录\n2. 进行市场分析，识别5个新机会\n3. 生成5个SKILL.md文件\n4. 推送到GitHub\n5. 更新Registry\n6. 返回报告\n\n让我开始执行任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在开始执行第二批次任务。首先创建目录并进行市场分析："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/batch-2026-03-05-2"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":4461,"output":206,"cacheRead":9984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14651,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772721015956}}
